snippet.title: Dieselpunk Wars - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/952240/Dieselpunk_Wars/
Our Kickstarter campaign was a success! Thank you to all our backers!

Dieselpunk Wars is a sandbox vehicle building game, focused on combat with advanced physics and damage simulation. Use over 300 elements to build a war machine of your dreams. Construct vehicles that ride on the ground, soar through the skies, or dive underwater. Prepare for combat and test your skills!

#Dieselpunk Wars
Kickstarter: https://kickstarter.com/projects/playway/dieselpunk-wars
Discord: https://bit.ly/DPWDiscord
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DieselpunkWars/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DieselpunkWars
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/DieselpunkWars/
